node.text:
New YouTube video up! Link in my bio. 

I learn how to fell a giant ash tree... and drive a tractor... and mill a log with @crauber and his dad. 

If you’re feeling the heat of summer, this footage from upstate NY in January is sure to cool you off 😂❄️🥶

Hope y’all enjoy! 
#treefelling #chainsaw #milling #ashtree #woodworker #thesource #socold

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Ashley Harwood on July 27, 2021 tagging @ashleyharwoodturning. May be an image of 1 person, dog and indoor.

node.text: Turner Update: She did great in her surgery today! X-rays look good of her head and chest. We may need some additional tests to see if it’s gone up into her sinuses. Should find out results of the biopsy by tomorrow. Glad to have her home and resting! Also pictured is an awesome #kumiko screen that my grandparents brought back from Japan while my grandfather was stationed in the Pacific during WWII. Turner keeps it safe 😊 #twoturners #sweetgirl #dogsofinsta

node.text: On a personal note: my girl Turner is going in for a surgery tomorrow. She has a mass on her upper jaw that needs to be removed and tested.
